(# Odoo Support Scope V1.1 \(7 April 2026\) - Simple Hindi Guide) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 1\) Yeh document kis liye hai?) Tj
T*
(Yeh guide Aha! Consulting ke Odoo support scope ko **simple language** mein explain karti) Tj
T*
(hai, taaki management, admin team aur technical team sab easily samajh saken.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 2\) Overarching Requirements \(High-Level Rules\)) Tj
T*
(1. Current Odoo version: **V19**.) Tj
T*
(2. Saara kaam future upgrades ke liye compatible hona chahiye.) Tj
T*
(3. Existing database integrity aur customizations ko damage nahi hona chahiye.) Tj
T*
(4. Naya kaam existing live Odoo ko break kiye bina deploy hona chahiye.) Tj
T*
(5. Hosting currently custom server par hai:  ) Tj
T*
(   **https://portal.ahaconsulting.net.au/**) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 3\) IP, License aur Responsibility) Tj
T*
(1. Jo code/work banega uski IP Aha! Consulting ki hogi.) Tj
T*
(2. Code reuse pe koi ongoing fee nahi.) Tj
T*
(3. Aisa code nahi banana jo third-party paid dependency force kare.) Tj
T*
(4. Agar existing customized code ko damage hota hai, to repair no extra cost par hona) Tj
T*
(chahiye.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 4\) Priority 1 - Stripe Credit Card Fee \(1.5%\)) Tj
T*
(### Business Need) Tj
T*
(Company chahti hai ki payment external custom Stripe portal ki jagah **standard Odoo portal) Tj
T*
(flow** se ho, jisse reporting clean ho aur bugs kam hon.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Required Behavior) Tj
T*
(Jab customer credit card \(Stripe\) choose kare:) Tj
T*
(1. **1.5% surcharge** auto calculate ho.) Tj
T*
(2. Invoice mein auto ek alag line item add ho.) Tj
T*
(3. Customer checkbox se acknowledge kare ki credit card fee apply hogi.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Yeh flow 3 jagah kaam kare) Tj
T*
(1. Pay an Invoice) Tj
T*
(2. Book and Pay for Training) Tj
T*
(3. Purchase a Product) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Existing stripe link \(reference\):  ) Tj
T*
(https://www.ahaconsulting.net.au/stripe-payment) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Suggested Technical Approach \(Odoo V19-compatible\)) Tj
T*
(- Company settings mein fee rate field maintain karein \(example: 1.5\).) Tj
ET
endstream
