T*
(## 5\) Priority 2 - Training Courses Display) Tj
T*
(### Goal) Tj
T*
(Website par do views hone chahiye:) Tj
T*
(1. **Upcoming events** \(scheduled with date\)) Tj
T*
(2. **Course portfolio** \(evergreen catalog, even if unscheduled\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Filters required) Tj
T*
(- Provider type:) Tj
T*
(  - Aha Academy: public full visibility + booking allowed) Tj
T*
(  - IAP2: public ko limited details; full course/price login ke baad) Tj
T*
(- Content type:) Tj
T*
(  - Engagement, Conflict, Facilitation, Evaluation) Tj
T*
(- Extra actions:) Tj
T*
(  - Booking link) Tj
T*
(  - Downloadable PDF) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Odoo standard limitation \(important\)) Tj
T*
(- Odoo standard mein login-status ke base par specific field hide/show direct config se) Tj
T*
(limited hota hai.) Tj
T*
(- Event ko website par dikhane ke liye date required hoti hai.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Practical Solution) Tj
T*
(1. Event Tags se provider/content filters implement karein.) Tj
T*
(2. Login-based visibility ke liye custom website template logic add karein.) Tj
T*
(3. ?Portfolio? ke liye separate website model/page banayein jahan unscheduled courses bhi) Tj
T*
(visible hon.) Tj
T*
(4. Event records ke liye scheduled/unscheduled + publish/unpublish toggles add karein.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 6\) Priority 3 - Past Work Catalog) Tj
T*
(### Requirement) Tj
T*
(Public-facing ?Past Work? page jisme:) Tj
T*
(- Filter by **Sector**) Tj
T*
(- Filter by **Type of Work**) Tj
T*
(- Dono filters ek saath kaam karein) Tj
T*
(- Dynamic results aayein \(page reload dependent static listing na ho\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### Content Source) Tj
T*
(- Spreadsheet-driven data \(name, categories, images, PDF links, etc.\)) Tj
T*
(- Non-technical team easily update kar sake) Tj
ET
endstream
